I just proudly voted to pass the One Big Beautiful Bill Act – bringing us another step closer to delivering meaningful results for the American people, especially those in the Third District. This legislation:

✅ Provides Americans tax relief and opportunities for economic growth;
✅ Prevents waste, fraud, and abuse of critical government resources;
✅ Invests in our military;
✅ Secures our border;
✅Unleashes American energy; and much more.

The exploding national debt is one of the greatest threats to our country. America's challenges will be impossible to address if we continue down an unsustainable path.

@RepEdCase and I proposed a framework to tackle this issue. Read more from @stevebrawner ⬇️
